- Kubernetes has a new metric called Millicores that is used to measure CPU usage. It is a CPU core split into 1000 units (milli = 1000).

- Deamonset - Deploy a pod on each and every node (each node need exactly one instance of the pod). 
Example: kube-proxy, or pod that run to collect log and resource of each node

- Job resource - One the job done, the pod is consider complete. 
- CronJob 